des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. Name an undergraduate, a student of modern sciences, a progressive eagar to join the mainstream, but yet unable to face the world, seeking refuge in a theory of race, origin and glory! 
Are you such a person, then help is available to transcend the dim conditioning of this programming, as you learn to erase the scripts of this autopilot thinking.
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
